        Start A Campaign 
      %ul.features.list-inline
        %li
          %h3
            %i.fa.fa-check
            Launch Advocacy Websites
          %p Create customized action sites, including petitions, polls, events, and more, for supporter acquisition and engagement.
        %li
          %h3
            %i.fa.fa-tablet
            Recruit New Supporters
          %p Learn about the interests, locations, and even Facebook friends of your supporters, as well as the best email address to contact them.
